WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.266 --> 00:00:01.101
[yelps]

00:00:01.134 --> 00:00:02.135
<i> Understanding
 of the human mind</i>

00:00:02.168 --> 00:00:04.370
<i> isn't complete unless it
 considers everything</i>

00:00:04.403 --> 00:00:06.305
the brain is capable of.

00:00:06.338 --> 00:00:08.241
♪♪

00:00:11.811 --> 00:00:16.082
When is it okay to risk harm
in the name of science?

00:00:16.115 --> 00:00:18.418
♪♪

00:00:18.451 --> 00:00:19.519
I'm about to find out.

00:00:19.552 --> 00:00:23.089
♪♪

00:00:23.122 --> 00:00:24.624
I'm a little anxious about
what's about to happen.

00:00:24.657 --> 00:00:28.061
This will probably be
a little bit uncomfortable.

00:00:28.094 --> 00:00:29.328
And my job?

00:00:29.361 --> 00:00:31.364
I'm the lab rat.

00:00:33.165 --> 00:00:34.700
<i> I'm about to head up
 the Amazon to drink</i>

00:00:34.733 --> 00:00:36.836
<i> an ancient psychedelic drug.</i>

00:00:36.869 --> 00:00:38.571
I would suggest that

00:00:38.604 --> 00:00:41.474
<i> you think about
 an emotional intention.</i>

00:00:41.507 --> 00:00:42.275
To make it emotional

00:00:42.308 --> 00:00:44.177
is a lot more frightening
to me.

00:00:44.210 --> 00:00:45.411
♪♪

00:00:45.444 --> 00:00:48.448
<i> I started to see
 my body disappearing.</i>

00:00:48.481 --> 00:00:50.216
♪♪

00:00:50.249 --> 00:00:52.085
<i> There was no going back.</i>

00:00:52.885 --> 00:00:55.121
<i> You're forced to see
 the world differently,</i>

00:00:55.154 --> 00:00:56.456
and by seeing the world
differently,

00:00:56.489 --> 00:00:58.158
<i> it makes you think
 differently.</i>

00:00:59.391 --> 00:01:00.225
<i> What I wanna know is,</i>

00:01:00.259 --> 00:01:01.861
if we put them
in front of a switch,

00:01:01.894 --> 00:01:03.830
<i> watching a train barrelling
 towards people,</i>

00:01:03.863 --> 00:01:06.099
<i> would they actually
 pull it?</i>

00:01:06.132 --> 00:01:09.202
I bet a lot of them
would freeze in that moment.

00:01:09.235 --> 00:01:11.537
♪♪

00:01:11.570 --> 00:01:13.673
<i> This isn't about
 having fun.</i>

00:01:14.340 --> 00:01:15.341
It's for science.

00:01:15.374 --> 00:01:16.876
♪♪

00:01:16.909 --> 00:01:17.743
I hope.

00:01:17.776 --> 00:01:19.445
♪♪

00:01:19.478 --> 00:01:21.581
[all gasping]

00:01:21.614 --> 00:01:31.658
♪♪

00:01:31.658 --> 00:01:36.663
♪♪

